{"id":"5e9c32859b6559241525deed","artists":["5e9b69577a1236eccfeb269a"],"title":"Single Of The Week: Twin Shadow – Castles In The Snow","content":"<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-3752\" href=\"https://admin.</p><p>crackintheroad.com/music/3667-single-of-the-week-twin-shadow-castles-in-the-snow/attachment/twinshadow3copyrightsamanthawest_cropped\"><img class=\"alignnone size-totallysizedforever wp-image-3752\" title=\"TwinShadow3copyrightSamanthaWest_cropped\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/uploads/2010/12/TwinShadow3copyrightSamanthaWest_cropped-740x602.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"740\" height=\"602\" /></a></p>\n<p>For an artist that so quickly surged to critical acclaim, <strong>Twin Shadow</strong> has been somewhat absent from the pages of <strong>Crack in the Road</strong>. So it seems aptly fitting now to credit him with our single of the week. <em>Castles In The Snow</em> taken from <strong>Twin Shadow’s</strong> debut record <em>Forget</em>, is as much a brilliant pop song as it is an abstract observational confession. Full of hauntingly majestic imagery, it clings to the brain after the first listen, with little blemishes of S<strong>hadow’s</strong> past being fully realised in front of us. One to watch, if you weren’t already. Have a great week. J</p>\n<p><object classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" codebase=\"https://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F5342702&secret_url=false\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" src=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F5342702&secret_url=false\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\"></embed></object> <span><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/hypetrak/twin-shadow-castles-in-the-snow\">